{"tid":1516991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麗晶風暴 被問麗晶突改密碼 瑞安羅寶瑜笑而不語","createTime":"2019-08-29T18:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T18:49:18.000Z","uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3930a475bb70c914d67fac9d869b4a634a67dc68","tid":1516991,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"瑞安羅寶瑜笑而不語,禁都得?! <br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】啱啱過咗嘅星期六，九龍灣麗晶花園發生離奇事件，居民投訴瑞安集團旗下瑞安建業(0983)擁有的管理公司臨時更改密碼，又唔通知住戶新密碼，搞到居民冇得返屋企。噚日瑞安集團另一家上市公司瑞安房地產（0272）舉行中期業績發布會，傳媒關注更改密碼事件，主席羅康瑞罕有咁缺席發布會，反而由佢個女、執行董事羅寶瑜代父出征，連同多名管理層主持大會。在場公關一見有記者提問麗晶花園件事，就以瑞房及內地業務為由擋駕，最終無回答記者嘅提問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/經濟/article/20190829/s00004/1567015827776/被問麗晶突改密碼-瑞安羅寶瑜笑而不語\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%2Farticle%2F20190829%2Fs00004%2F1567015827776%2F%E8%A2%AB%E5%95%8F%E9%BA%97%E6%99%B6%E7%AA%81%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC-%E7%91%9E%E5%AE%89%E7%BE%85%E5%AF%B6%E7%91%9C%E7%AC%91%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%9E&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=87dfac5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%2Farticle%2F20190829%2Fs00004%2F1567015827776%2F%E8%A2%AB%E5%95%8F%E9%BA%97%E6%99%B6%E7%AA%81%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC-%E7%91%9E%E5%AE%89%E7%BE%85%E5%AF%B6%E7%91%9C%E7%AC%91%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%9E&h=55bc8376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/經濟/article/20190829/s00004/1567015827776/被問麗晶突改密碼-瑞安羅寶瑜笑而不語</a>"},{"pid":"f55fedcc6c0cba66058c74dd30ac00147296dde7","tid":1516991,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T18:41:43.000Z","msg":"出錢玩鳩自己 買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8550d76b4e59ba8d850f061038e462fbe3458b3","tid":1516991,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f55fedcc6c0cba66058c74dd30ac00147296dde7","tid":1516991,"uid":14494,"like":1,"di